divs: Sighting DetailsI was inside my house praying when I saw a bright but small green light pass over. I couldn't decide if it was a shooting star or a UFO. I flew pretty fast, has 1 observed green light on the side, it seemed like it had apeared out of nowhere because I noticed it at the corner of my eye. I was kind of shocked. It then disapeared.
Summary: going fast, green light, apeared out of nowhere, looked kinda like a shooting star.
